spec_data.Name: mingw32-libgovirt-static
spec_data.Description:
libgovirt is a library that allows applications to use oVirt REST API
to list VMs managed by an oVirt instance, and to get the connection
parameters needed to make a SPICE/VNC connection to them.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 27 Jul 2017 09:22:06 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: MinGW support for a GObject library for interacting with oVirt REST API
